@startuml
title RabbitMQ Class Diagram

class Producer {
  +publish(message, exchange, routingKey)
}

class Exchange {
  -name
  -type
  +route(message)
}

class Queue {
  -name
  +enqueue(message)
  +dequeue()
}

class Consumer {
  +consume(queue)
  +ack(message)
}

class Message {
  -headers
  -body
  -routingKey
}

Producer --> Exchange : publish()
Exchange --> Queue : route()
Queue --> Consumer : deliver()
Consumer --> Queue : ack()

@enduml
